<div class="card-base w-full rounded-[var(--radius-large)] overflow-hidden relative mb-4 onload-animation bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 dark:from-gray-800 dark:to-gray-750 border-l-4 border-blue-500">
    <div class="pl-6 pr-6 py-5 flex items-center gap-3">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M11 5H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v11a2 2 0 002 2h11a2 2 0 002-2v-5m-1.414-9.414a2 2 0 112.828 2.828L11.828 15H9v-2.828l8.586-8.586z"></path>
            </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="flex-1">
            <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed">
                <span class="font-semibold text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400">公告：</span>
                手机端可以点击右上角打开菜单，浏览更多功能。
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 hidden md:block">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
